; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tAfford<br />\n\tTo afford means to have the ability to provide or supply. Who can afford? What can be afforded? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They can afford it... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) afford housing<br />\n\t2) afford medical care<br />\n\t3) afford the consequences<br />\n\t4) afford <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/backlash\" target=\"_blank\">backlash</a><br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tFive seconds, he would give himself five seconds to search for the cap. With his estimate of the distance between the department door and the team leader's office door, Doug figured he could afford five seconds. If the cap bottle could not be found within these few seconds, he was getting out regardless. In this short duration, Doug listened attentively for the opening of the department door. Although there was quite a distance in between, because of the stillness of the surrounding, even a slight sound carried an each and could be heard fairly well.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167186327216/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjen